data.description: Relax you have found it! This home is an oasis of tranquility with ample amounts of space. Five bedroom, three full bath ranch home with just over 2,000 square feet! Large backyard with plenty of space for your family, pets, and so much more. Don't walk, run to your new home! Two private driveways and NO HOA, bring your camper or boat or family and friends. Just minutes from shopping, neutral location allows quick access into close cities such as Atlanta and Smyrna.
